A split-screen workspace viewed from above in Studio Ghibli style, showing a cozy developer's desk with a massive curved monitor divided into two halves - one side displaying cascading green checkmarks flowing like magical particles, the other side showing red X symbols transforming into butterflies. Warm afternoon light streams through a window where a small spirit creature sits watching. Coffee cup with steam forming swirling patterns, scattered programming books with weathered spines, and a determined cat sleeping on mechanical keyboard. Soft watercolor textures, whimsical atmosphere, gentle shadows, muted earth tones mixed with pops of green and red representing passing and failing states.
